  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Partnership to Engage, Reform and Learn (PERL)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The programme works with government and civil society at federal and state levels to reduce inefficiency and corruption in the use of Nigerian resources and therefore improve delivery of services, including for women, girls and persons with disability. It does this in partnership with other DFID programmes supporting service delivery by helping Nigerian stakeholders improve accountability for use of resources including improving processes for raising revenue, allocating resources, planning and programme implementation.</narrative>
  </description>
